did.unittitle: Ross, Elaine M. Will the Wind Whisper? for Mezzo-Soprano and Piano

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Pieces included: 1 score, 1 CD. Notes: The CD and score were in a manila envelope on which was written "Kentucky New Music Festival, Sop/Mz-sop submissions." CD includes two other pieces: Shapeshifter, for flute and piano, and Mystic Rhythm, for flute, alto saxophone and two marimbas..
